header.gameNote: HOOPS FOR HOPE CLASSIC AT PUERTO VALLARTA Mexico

article.headline: Rider 86, Jacksonville 71
article.story: PUERTO VALLARTA, Mexico -- Anthony Myles scored 23 points to help Rider defeat Jacksonville 86-71 on Friday in the Hoops for Hope Classic. Myles was 7 of 12 from the field and had nine rebounds. Myles was 3 of 4 from 3-point range. Jonathon Thompson scored 18 and Nurideen Lindsey added 10 for the Broncos (3-3). Rider led 34-26 at halftime, only trailing early in the first half. Glenn Powell led Jacksonville (2-4) with 22 points and 12 rebounds. Keith McDougald had 20 and Jarvis Haywood added 12.
